{
  "stem": "5388.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, dangerous as can be to cross between the-- she used to come on Friday morning to help Mother prepare the Sabbath.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, it's as crazy as can be.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You couldn't believe it if you wouldn't have seen it yourself with your own eyes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she did it twice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the third time, she came, Father said, now that's it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "OK, no more of this nonsense.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And as a matter of fact, later on before they even took the Jews away from Suwalki and took them in November, in '41 to Biala Podlaska around, I think, Lublin type of neighborhoods.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] They took the Jews of Raczki, dumped them on the border between the-- between Raczki and Augustow.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they say, here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We don't want them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You can have them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And so they came in and the Russians took them, and they were in-- and that's how some of the people that were with us in Slonim from Raczki, that's how they wound up in Augustow.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We lived in a number of places.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "First, we lived in one place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a house.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had the merchandise, so the Russians came in without.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was a line, buying everything in sight.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Whether it's for clothes or whether it's for-- for dresses or for shirts, anything in sight.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So a lot of merchandise was sold.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's how we lived during the war, that Father had the money that he preserved from this-- from the sales.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we moved outside suddenly in 1940.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a real cold winter, as can be.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember it was below 30 centigrade, which is-- I don't know, figure it out.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
